      1          /**
      2           *  @file		DoorOpeningSystemMonitor.c
      3           *
      4           *  @brief		A monitor that manages the Door Opening System device, together with the DOS Push and DOS Pull tasks.
      5           *
      6           *  @details    Door Opening System (briefly DOS) is a device used to assist with the drying by opening the door of the dishwasher
      7           *  			releasing the moisture out of the tub at selected moment given by the cycle design.
      8           *  			Door Opening System monitor is used for the DOS overall management, and exchanges data with the DOS Push
      9           *  			and DOS Pull tasks, that are used to trigger the activation of the Push and of the Pull sequences.
     10           *
     11           */
     12          
