    160          /**
    161           * It implements the execution of the Door Opening System Monitor.
    162           * It manages the execution of the Pull sequence (that can be started either by DOS Pull task or
    163           * inside RunExit) and updates the DOS_Pin_State.
    164           * The Pull sequence consists of 2 sequential steps, whose duration is specified by setting file parameters:
    165           * - Off: the DOS output is driven off.
    166           * - On: the DOS output is driven on.
    167           * This sequence is processed by the DOS device controller to pull in the device pin.
    168           *
    169           * @return None
    170           *
    171           */

